data.meta_description: Hilda Agnes Mary WISE was born on March 28, 1911 in Longford, Tasmania, Australia, daughter of George Robert Thomas WISE and Hilda May BANFIELD. She died on December 19, 1962 in Hobart, Tasmania, Australia. This information is part of More like a forest than a tree! by Karen M Hughes on Genealogy Online.
